────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
EXCLUDED COMPONENTS (NOT distributed with this repository)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
The institution-specific Electronic Health Record (EHR/HBYS) scraping and
ingestion scripts (scripts/cerebral_*.py), authentication cookies, the
Turkish drug database (ilac.json), and any cached patient data are
intentionally excluded from this distribution and remain local-only.
See docs/EHR_ADAPTER.md for how to build a compliant adapter for your own
EHR system.

